description_text:
Senior IT Recruitment Specialist
Warsaw, Poland
Job ID:
11345
Senior IT Recruitment Specialist
Location: Warszawa
Senior IT Recruitment Specialist contributes by attracting, sourcing and recruiting diverse pools of top IT talent for current and future organizational needs (Permanent Placement & IT Contracting).
Responsibilities:
Conduct recruitment activities for IT positions (e2e) including candidate sourcing, resume screening, phone screening, and on-line interviews;
Ensure applicants match experience with specific job-related requirements;
Proactively source, identify, and recruit passive candidates utilizing a variety of sourcing methods such as networking and internet recruiting to build strong, timely pipelines for open positions;
Negotiate and prepare employment offers;
Building relationships with candidates.
Requirements:
3+ years of experience in recruitment area;
Experience with various interview formats, including phone screening calls, on-line interviews, etc.;
Experience evaluating IT candidates;
Excellent communication and relationship-building skills;
Solid organizational and time-management abilities;
English: B2.
We offer:
Long-term & stable cooperation (Contract of Employment);
Professional development and support of Adecco’s Consultants and experienced Managers;
Enhance your expertise in the IT area;
Office in the heart of Warsaw (Plac Europejski 2); hybrid model;
Medical, Insurance & Multisport Package;
Trainings & Webinars.
Apply Now

